              My expertise spans a variety of technologies, including HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and frameworks like React and Angular on the front-end, as well as Node.js, Express, and databases like MongoDB and MySQL on the back-end. This comprehensive skill set enables me to design, develop, and deploy fully functional web applications that meet modern standards.
              
